| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4388 — Recovery Inhibition (payoutsking)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 81e8d5a8-4482-5d25-a931-cd2b1c8a30f3"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
